line_1: So when with greatest Zeal we Heaven accost,
line_2: Our Notions all in Extacies are lost,

line_1: So when with greatest Zeal we Heaven accost,
line_2: We utter least, where it deserves the most.

line_1: And when they kindly turn'd them to accost
line_2: The prince, they almost pierc'd him with their frost.
